data.title: Anthony Lamond
data.meta_description: Anthony Lamond uses Humanitix for their events. Discover events by Anthony Lamond, learn more, or contact this host.
data.text:
POWERED BY Humanitix logo

Tickets for good, not greed! Humanitix dedicates 100% of profits to charities providing education, healthcare and basic necessities to humans across the globe

Anthony Lamond is one of Australia's hardest working and much admired Stand-Up Comedian having Hosted and Produced over 750 Shows all around Australia. He has produced shows and shared the stage with high profile Comedians such as Dave Hughes, Jimeoin, Arj Barker Fiona O'Loughlin, Peter Rowsthorn, Cal Wilson, Merrick Watts, Lawrence Mooney, The Old Fella, Chris Franklin, Heath Franklin and Bob Franklin just to name a few.
